snippet.title: Still Hunt gameplay (PC Game, 1996)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Still Hunt, Dos PC game produced by HiCom in 1996 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/still-hunt/15567/
Still Hunt is a side-scrolling shooter very good. The player can choose between the male and female protagonists, who defend their homeland against an onslaught of mechanized creatures.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
